## Frontend — React 19 + Cloudflare Workers

**Node ≥ 20** · **TypeScript strict** · **Vite 8** · **React Router 7** (loaders)

### UI & styling

| Layer | Choice |
| --- | --- |
| Components | shadcn/ui Nova preset (Radix), `@/components/ui/*` |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 |
| Icons | Lucide |
| Font | Geist Variable |
| Forms | react-hook-form + Zod |
| Theme | next-themes (synced with `user.theme` via PATCH /api/me) |
| Toasts | sonner |

### Routing

- Public: `/`, `/es` — `LocaleLayout`, `PageSeo`, indexable routes in `src/seo/pages.ts`
- App: `/app/*` — `requireAuth` loader (user + credits), `AppLayout` outlet context
- Settings: `/app/settings/*` — sessions, accounts, credits, api-keys
- Login: `window.location` to `VITE_API_URL/auth/google`

### API client (`src/lib/api.ts`)

- Base: `import.meta.env.VITE_API_URL`
- All calls: `credentials: "include"`
- `api.me()` / `updateMe()` parse with `userSchema.strict()` (Zod)
- Credits loader returns `null` on failure (not fake zero)
- Validate: `POST /v1/validate` + `X-Idempotency-Key`

### i18n

- i18next + HTTP backend: `/locales/{{lng}}/{{ns}}.json`
- Namespaces: `common`, `app`, `seo`
- Languages: `en` (source), `es` — always update both
- Static `t('key')` only (no dynamic keys — i18n-check)

### Contracts

Only `contracts/user.json` synced (`make sync-contracts` from workspace root). Other API shapes are TypeScript interfaces in `api.ts`.

### Build & deploy

| Piece | Role |
| --- | --- |
| `@cloudflare/vite-plugin` | Workers + client build |
| `worker/index.ts` | asset serving, security headers, 404 routing |
| wrangler | `npm run deploy` → `front` worker |
| `prebuild` | sitemap generation |

Build-time env: `VITE_API_URL`, `VITE_SITE_URL`, `VITE_SITE_NAME`, `VITE_OG_IMAGE`, etc.

### Tooling & CI

| Tool | Role |
| --- | --- |
| Husky + lint-staged | pre-commit format/lint on staged files |
| commitlint | Conventional Commits |
| GitHub Actions | `npm ci` + `npm run validate` |

### Verify

```bash
cd mails-frontend
npm run validate   # format, lint, i18n, seo, api contracts, typecheck, test, build
```

