## Cross-stack integration

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  Browser --> CFWorker[Cloudflare Workers SPA]
  Browser -->|credentials include| FlyAPI[Fly Go API]
  FlyAPI --> Postgres[(Postgres)]
  FlyAPI --> Stripe[Stripe API]
  FlyAPI --> Google[Google OAuth]
```

| Concern | Pattern |
| --- | --- |
| User API shape change | migration → sqlc → handler `UserJSON` → `contracts/user.json` → `make sync-contracts` → Zod `userSchema` → `api.ts` |
| Push order | `back` before `front` when API/migrations change |
| Local dev | `make dev` (Overmind: backend :3000 + frontend :3001) |
| Contract sync | `make sync-contracts` from workspace root |

### Commit format

- Backend: `feat|fix|chore|docs|refactor|test|ci|perf` (Lefthook)
- Frontend: `feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|perf|test|build|ci|chore|revert` (Husky)

Commit and push **inside each child repo**, not from meta-repo (except docs in workspace root).
